\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little bit of regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 When I went to Market Rasen school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 What were you doing then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well I - the - I used to - we used to leave school at four, and then I used to meet the twenty 
to five grain at Market Rasen station and collect the whole evening paper, and I used to sell them on the way home. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 How did you get this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 A man came to the school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 How long did it take you, what hours did you work to do this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well I used to - take me an hour sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 What happened about the Saturday paper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 I got it, I used to go in and get it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 How much did you get a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 I used to get - I made about - four or five shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did you feel this was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well it was in those days. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Some of it, but I - I saved it up and bought a bicycle with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 You didn't work with anybody else did you, you were on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 On the papers, yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 How did you feel your employer treated you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 How did you feel about selling papers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well I didn't mind it for - it was - earned me a few coppers and suchlike as that you see and - and 
I could get off the like and leave them on the way home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did the job alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did you have any other part time jobs before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 What was your first full time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well I was - I went apprentice to Market Rasen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 What sort of apprentice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 
Drapery. I lived in there. Worked four year for nothing. Yes. Remember paying sixty pound premium. And now they get about six pound a week now don't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well - me mother - went down with me mother and found - went and asked 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 So they sort of saw you through it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Can you tell me what exactly you did in the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Oh anything. Anything there was to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Was it a big sort of drapery?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Not a big place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 How many apprentices would there have been, one at a time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well - had - had three. We had a grocery - it was grocery and drapery you see. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 And you lived in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did they feed you well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Oh yes.
