\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Oh - half past seven in the morning. And - Saturdays, sometimes nearly twelve when we finished at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did you get a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did you ever have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 I got no pay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did you get any days off?
