\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well you felt it at first but you soon got used to it. Y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3688485\charrsid8982218 es}{\rtlch\fcs1 
