 stories. Only - only his daughter used to be - assisted in the shop you see. Yes. And - I was talking to her one day in the shop and he came in. He said, well introduce - introduce me to him. He said, you needn't introduce me, I said, I've known you year
s. Yes, and then Inspector Atkinson, I knew him well. And then there was another police constable, well he came from Dailsdon, the next village to mine.
