\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well - I hadn't any views, I didn't bother with - politics really.
