\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well it was directly I left school. Well - it was either football, cricket or tennis.
