Well, they Doyle Carte when they came we used to always go to them you see. And if we wanted a real - night out as you can say, there used to be about six of us, we used to go to the Grand - Grand Theatre, you know where it was. We used to go there for a
 night out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 What about the Empire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 That was very good. Used to go there very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 You made new friends because it was a different part of the world for you, how did you meet your new friends?
