\insrsid3688485\charrsid8982218 Jessup\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 . They used to come in. 'Cos we knew them then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 How did you meet your wife?
