day in the village. And when - I went to it - of course they didn't know I could dance at all. 'Cos I had - a friend - good friends in Market Rasen you see where the other apprentice, and I used to go to dancing class there, well they didn't know. So - wh
en - I was sitting with them round the hall. And one of these ladies - anyway she came up and - come, let's - let's have this dance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 She asked you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Yes. Well we were friends do you see. We used to same dancing class as I did. We were there - he s
ays - father says, he can't dance. I could you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 What dances were they then?
