Didn't have none of those quick steps and that you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 When you were an apprentice fairly near home did your parents meet your friends?
