Oh yes, we used to go - well there was - there was one of my friends - he come from - Swineshead near Boston and another one came from Alford, and one from Hegginham. Well we used to take it in turns to - we us
ed to go to Eggerton Feast and Kislby Feast and - Alford Fair. We used to go for a weekend. They used to go with me and I used to go with them. Yes, we had a good time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did your parents expect to know where you were?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well they didn't bother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Did they expect you to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Not particular - wasn't particular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Do you know if they expected your sister to be in by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Well they expected her - they didn't bother you see not in the village. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Were boys and girls treated very differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 No. No, we all mixed together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 You didn't feel the girls were more protected than the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Can you tell me about your sister getting married? How you didn't know the name of her husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 
Yes. No, I didn't know. 'Cos I knew him as Billie Smith you see. And of course his proper names was Bill Orton. And she used to tell her friends and that - well when I knew she was engaged but - she said she wouldn't marry him, never marry
 Bill Smith she said. Well she didn't, it were Bill Orton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11629161 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 What did you most enjoy in your free time when you were a young man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4396391 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 Oh I liked football. 'Course in the summertime used to - play a lot of tennis at night. 'Cos the - on the Castle Boulevard, that was - }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3688485\charrsid8982218 Jessup\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9441483\charrsid8982218 
 place you see for the ladies to sleep. And they'd a good tennis court down there and we - used it when we wanted it. Yes, and then there's - caves and that down there you see, we had a good time down there.
